title: Celebrity Gossip 2- Jury Has A Verdict For R. Kelly
description: Yesterday we spent the morning wondering if Travis Barker was okay after being rushed to the hospital, and it seems we finally have some answers. Plus, a jury in New York has decided on R Kelly’s fate.
